    dc:creator "Bernot, James P.", "Boxshall, Geoff", "Ismail, Norshida", "Nishida, Yusuke", "Ohtsuka, Susumu" ;
    dc:date "2024" ;
    dc:title "First record of Caligus dussumieri Rangnekar, 1957 (Copepoda, Siphonostomatoida, Caligidae) from Malaysia, with notes on caligids found from Malaysia and on host-specificity of caligids on lutjanid fishes" ;
    bibo:endPage "116598" ;
    bibo:journal "Biodiversity Data Journal" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2024-02-20" ;
    bibo:startPage "116598" ;
    bibo:volume "12" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.12.e116598.figure1>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.12.e116598.figure2>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.12.e116598.figure3>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.12.e116598.figure4>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.12.e116598.figure5> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.12.e116598.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Caligus dussumieri Rangnekar, 1957, adult female. A Habitus, dorsal view; B Antennule; C Antenna; D Mandible; E Maxilla; F Maxilliped; G Sternal furca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/932839" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.12.e116598.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. CLSM images of Caligus dussumieri Rangnekar, 1957. A Exopod of leg 1, showing spinular ornamentation on plumose setae along posterior margin; B Rami of leg 2 showing ornamentation on outer margin of endopod and spatulate spine on first exopodal segment." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/932843" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.12.e116598.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. CLSM images of Caligus dussumieri Rangnekar, 1957. A dorsal view; B ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/932840" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.12.e116598.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Caligus dussumieri Rangnekar, 1957 adult female. A Leg 1, a Four terminal elements of Leg 1; B Leg 2." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/936448" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.12.e116598.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Caligus dussumieri Rangnekar, 1957, adult female. A Leg 3, a Proximal segment of leg 3 exopod; B Leg 4, b Distal elements of Leg 4 second segment." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/936449" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

